Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在东京租界确认到巨大的爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据推测是报告中提到的Freyja弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍滞留在神根岛是否妥当?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无妨 一切都交给修奈泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般市民当场死亡人数逾千万
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事后受害者推测将达到2500万人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为医疗设施也被完全破坏 无法对市民进行及时救治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东京租界已死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是…我…干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这已经不是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再次使用这种兵器 黑骑士团将全军覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 眼下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军降落至东京租界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 朝比奈遇难 除此之外还有众多牺牲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.09,0:01:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管这些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最优先
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军动员搜寻娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个ZERO已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃亡者逃往左侧跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 请先重编军队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:02:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了 逃亡者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原以为逃走的是维蕾塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了 毫无节操的电视制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO干的吗 皇女殿下成了俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何不再给我多一点信任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准腿部 活捉她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是布里塔尼亚的外交特使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复 我们是布里塔尼亚的外交特使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无战斗意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外交特使?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水无濑 那台机体是通过正式管道申请的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 亲自深入敌人腹地?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂 叫你找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲自去指挥搜救部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 杰雷米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉一定还活着 找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后退至幕张后 重整战线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军紧急撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂 我叫你找娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要哥哥没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时休战是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么俾斯麦要撤兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因正在确认中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但似乎没有交战意向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 东京也暂时停战了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO的指示吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在哥哥身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不也就我们两人坚持至今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想让哥哥静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事等一下再说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 虽然也许没太大意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥这里有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会有它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是原本打算给娜娜莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休想代替娜娜莉 冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没察觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我痛恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深恶痛绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几次想害死你 不过未能如愿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出去 别再出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来 我仍旧没意识到 会造成怎样的损失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你必须做出选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是抛弃科学保留人心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是舍弃人心来投身科学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德老师也遇到过这种选择吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就道德败坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点自知之明还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我制造的Freyja
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 ZERO不接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有ZERO也得与修奈泽尔进行会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我们的头头是ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先斩后奏是不是有点不妥?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屠杀 妇女儿童一个不放过 是ZERO指使的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特哈尔特 为什么没有马上抓住修奈泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一架Knightmare护卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁这机会为朝比奈报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的专机上装载有Freyja弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Freyja?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引发刚才巨大爆炸的元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里爆炸的话 我们和ZERO都难以幸免
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知修奈泽尔打的什么算盘 但现在只能由我们去会会他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去检修回归的红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那交涉由我、千叶、迪特哈尔特 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 找不到扇那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉让大家担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉殿下 您一定要活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是我在教团中的所见所闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 忙着照顾你们打伤的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城 刚才我也说过请自觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:08:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是黑骑士团内务清洁副官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做为事务总长扇要的代理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的一厢情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 请务必到场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听闻是ZERO最元老级的志同道合者 身经百战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去 我曾被你所救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想来道一声谢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我和你之间的关系还真是奇妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运终究让我们成为敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须去找娜娜莉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸存者排队登录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姓名年龄住所血型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要救治的人去医务接待台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为避免混乱 请保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 你活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次和ZERO未分胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须先确认会谈内容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我想他也不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他并不是乐于与人讨论的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自背负一切 与他人疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这口吻貌似很熟悉ZERO的为人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比你更了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是我和科奈莉娅的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣布里塔尼亚帝国前第11皇子 鲁路修．V．布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最深爱却又敬畏的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是布里塔尼亚的皇子?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特哈尔特 你不可能毫无察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该从杰雷米亚和维蕾塔那里获得过情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白费心机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想靠这种言论令我们自乱阵脚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认可ZERO是因为他引发的奇迹而并非家谱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些奇迹如果有弄虚作假的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄虚作假?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO有特殊能力 GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强制对方服从命令的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以把它理解成一种强效的催眠术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这力量是奇迹之神?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少说我们家ZERO的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他天资聪颖胆识过人 可了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么皇子和GEASS 有证据吗 证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证据在此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维蕾塔也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真身是布里塔尼亚前皇子鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用GEASS的力量操纵人心的 骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO一直把我们蒙在鼓里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 把我们作为棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢 扇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这如果当真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 不能否认ZERO至今为止的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且如果真有GEASS的话 不是很令人鼓舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将成为对抗布里塔尼亚的强有力武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这份力量只对敌人使用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道对我们也是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他操纵自己的亲妹妹尤菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屠杀了前来参加日本特区的11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是正义的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要证据的话就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 你对尤菲使用了GEASS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她屠杀日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次屠杀是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而非我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO下令屠杀日本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是伪造的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是 被怀疑使用过GEASS的事件与人物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草壁 片濑少将也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也深受其害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来高亥的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚投降过来 全都得以说明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也无法保证自己有没有被他的GEASS操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想的话 着实可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:13:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们曾将Freyja弹头的事告知过ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为避免无谓的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot上留有通信纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 没有告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO无法信任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省悟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么的相信他….
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我们对他来说…只是棋子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生 ZERO这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位能否交出我的弟弟ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还有讨价还价的余地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿闻其详
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把日本还来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛自己曾经相信的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要换回日本 不然我无法原谅自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 请脱下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手构不着的话 我可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 无法触及之处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 能进来吗 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇希望你去四号仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四号?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体情况我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请脱下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我被抓住的时候 你们都做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 这个C.C. …
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你认识的C.C. 已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 不在 娜娜莉也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那鲁路修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉营救来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 我和娜娜莉谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她帮了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候说也许不合适 我的哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟将我们玩弄于鼓掌中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经知道你的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的英雄ZERO 壮志未成身先死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他勇敢的生前事迹 将被人们永久传颂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪特哈尔特 这就是你的剧本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本打算拍完你战胜布里塔尼亚的一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 节目被腰斩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 虽然Knightmare碍事 但扇他们毫无防备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷使用GEASS的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都那么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井上和吉田也是为你而死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 这样太单方面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏ZERO我们才走到今天不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也听他一言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和ZERO陪葬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会中了GEASS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说 我是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你干的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那看来没机会了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 事到如今才察觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不过是棋子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一颗特别优秀的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这不过是一盘棋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一场游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓 连蜃气楼一起解决
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥由我保护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了 蜃气楼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和巴别塔那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚 ZERO逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mordred能抓住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摧毁的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对守护领域的计算没想到这么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的哥哥果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 我已经没有活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 这动作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会让你死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大范围使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 这样下去你的心脏承受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全员 蜃气楼被偷走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有战斗单位全力摧毁蜃气楼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复 摧毁蜃气楼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直被人作为道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…住手 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是教团的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…救我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后又被哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确也许只是被哥哥利用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那段时光是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为那段回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于可以 成为人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 别使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:20:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 为什么救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是谎话吧 说什么想杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞒不过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对哥哥…最了解…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的哥哥是个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法确认目标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扩大搜索范围
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请增派地面班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉 罗洛 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是结局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 报应才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 正因为如此 谢谢 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救回的这条性命 对我来说还有必须做完的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到 会被迫使用这里的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸神的黄昏的接续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧的世界会被毁灭 新的世界将会被创造
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾父 查尔斯．D．布里塔尼亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:22:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去地狱的路上 少不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我和你到底是什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经知晓了真相  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.83,0:23:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,追随我到最后的 竟然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.56,0:23:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我总是后知后觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.82,0:24:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是鲁路修·Vi·布里塔尼亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而是鲁路修·兰佩路基的弟弟
